There are many things to keep a tourist busy in Velez Blanco! There are many ancient ruins to visit, grande expanses of beautiful desert, and sparkling beaches merrily adorned with festoons of garbage and filth left by the multitudes of scrambling tourists. If you wanted to have an unspoiled, clean and uncorrupted beachline, you'd need to find a place where humans haven't been yet. Sorry, but thats the truth.
